generated_code:
# solution.py
from typing import List, Optional, Dict, Set, Any

class Solution:
    def findSecret(self, text: str) -> str:
        # Split the input text into words
        words = text.split()
        
        # The secret word is the last word in the text
        secret_word = words[-1]
        
        # Return the secret word
        return secret_word
